        <h2>How to Start Your Hobby</h2>
        <p>It may be hard to find the motivation to start something but we have some simple tips to jump into a new hobby. First, you will want to decide what hobby you want to pursue. We suggest you take our Hobby Finder Quiz to get some ideas on what would be good to think about. Next, you will need to prepare. If supplies are needed, find some cheap starting supplies instead of investing in expensive supplies at first. Third, you jump right into it. No excuses, no waiting, just stepping into it.  </p> <br>
